text: Richard Frank "Dick" Celeste (born November 11, 1937) is an American politician from Ohio. He is a member of the Democratic Party. He served as the 64th Governor of Ohio from 1983 to 1991. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Governors of Ohio Category:Ambassadors of the United States Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from Cleveland Category:Lieutenant Governors of Ohio
